headline: New York’s top lawyer said Ethereum is a security. A crypto lawyer is coming for her job
summary: New York Attorney General Letitia James has warned against the unchecked growth of the crypto industry. A former Coinbase attorney is eyeing a longshot bid to replace her. “I'm not shying away from being seen as the crypto candidate,” he told DL News.

headline: Coinbase Completes Deribit Acquisition, Expands Global Crypto Derivatives Reach
summary: Coinbase Global, Inc. (NASDAQ:COIN) is holding steady in Friday's premarket trade after confirming the completion of its acquisition of crypto options leader Deribit. Barclays raised its price target for the stock from $352 to $365, while keeping its Equal Weight rating intact. The San Diego–based exchange announced Thursday that Deribit is now part of the Coinbase portfolio, cementing its position as one of the most comprehensive global crypto derivatives platforms.
